Class CompleteFreeSpaceExpansionRoom

  • java.lang.Object
    • autoroute.FreeSpaceExpansionRoom
      • autoroute.CompleteFreeSpaceExpansionRoom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompleteExpansionRoom, ExpansionRoom, SearchTreeObject, ShapeTree.Storable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>

    public class CompleteFreeSpaceExpansionRoom
extends FreeSpaceExpansionRoom
implements CompleteExpansionRoom, SearchTreeObject
    An expansion room, whose shape is completely calculated, so that it can be stored in a shape tree.
